content: पराचीन {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [पराच्-ख] {@--1@} Turned in an opposite direction, averted. {@--2@} Averse from, disinclined to. {@--3@} Not minding, not caring about. {@--4@} Happening subsequently or afterwards (उत्तरकालभव). {@--5@} Situated on the other side, being beyond. --नं {%<ab>ind.</ab>%} {@--1@} Away from, beyond. {@--2@} More than.
